also in the final confontation. I don't know where it comes from, but I'll try hard
to remove this bug. The loader works fine on A1200/68020, though.
Anyway, you can skip this part with the HELP key. I tested all the levels, and only those 2
caused crashes (I'm not faulty: the floppy version acts the same).

Please tell me if the faulty levels work on 68030 and 68040. I think this is a speed problem.


